title: Black Card, A3 Card 250GSM Thick Card Stock for Cards Making, Scrapbook, Office Printing and Arts or Crafts DIY (25 Sheets)
features: High Quality: Crafted from premium-quality material, our cardstock boasts a thickness of 92lb/250gsm, ensuring durability and sturdiness for all your crafting needs.

Versatile Usage: A3 Size(42cm×29.7cm), this card stock is perfect for a wide range of crafting projects including invitations, scrapbooking, crafting, DIY projects, decoration, and drawing, offering endless possibilities for creativity.

Durability: Designed to withstand cutting, adhering, and decorating, our cardstock ensures your creations maintain their integrity and beauty over time, making it the perfect choice for your creative projects.

Cut Freely: This card stock holds a nice sharp crease when folded and holds. It’s a great addition to your arts-and-crafts kit. Whether you use this cardstock for a wedding announcement or a party invitation, this paper is made to last without tearing or bending.

Great for Hobby Arts & Crafting: We recommend A4 card for hands-on crafting such as making stationery and greeting cards or even for sketching with pencil, marker pens, acrylic, watercolours, gouache, charcoal, pastels, gel pens, fine liners or calligraphy inks.
description: Product Description Why choose us among the wide range of coloured cardboards available in the market? The answer lies in the exceptional quality of our cardstock - every step of the way, from the carefully selected raw materials to the fine craftsmanship, ensures that it is durable and sturdy. Whether you are working as an art creator or are looking for a reliable multi-coloured cardstock, this cardstock is the ideal choice for you. You can also choose from A3 or A4 sizes and a wide range of colours to suit your creative and practical needs. Suitable for card making, collage etc. Suitable for cutting with scissors You can use cardstock folding to complete artwork that requires a sturdy task The cardstock is made of 250 GSM quality material, more thick and sturdy to better suit your creative needs.
